Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:05.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)}御法川报告 201X年 上海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,震惊涩谷的生化袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:10.11,Default2,,0000,0090,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}涩谷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.11,Default2,,0090,0000,0040,,{\1c&H0000FF&\fad(200,0)}生化袭击
